1. Layouts and Activities:
	
	- android activity: androud UI
	
	- android layouts:
	
		- RelativeLayout
		- FrameLayout
		- LinearLayout
		- Grid Layout
		- ViewPager
		- PagerTitleStrip
		
	- layout xml location: res/layout/activity_name.xml
	  e.g res/layout/activity_main.xml for main activity layout
	
	- <TextView /> -> display text
	
	- menu xml location: res/menu/activity_name.xml
	  e.g res/menu/main.xml for main activity menu
	  
	- <item /> -> menu item tag
	
	- string values location: res/values/string.xml
	
	- <ImageView /> -> display image
	
	- <Button /> -> display button
	
	- <VideoView /> -> display video
	
	- <ImageButton /> -> display button image
	
2. Intents and Events:

	- intents: interaction between activities